          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2016-03-07T19:53:40Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Small Aircraft Tax Modification Act of 2016</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand eligibility for the exemption from the excise tax on the transportation of persons and property by air by: (1)&nbsp;increasing the limit on the maximum certified takeoff weight of eligible aircraft not operated on an established line&nbsp;from 6,000 pounds or less to 12,500 pounds or less; and (2) providing that an aircraft shall not be considered as operated on an established line if it is performing an on-demand operation, as defined by regulation. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2016-02-10T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
